      "kd23": "Problems with your catheter site? (Peritoneal dialysis patients only)",
      "qh_15": "Some people are bothered by the effects of kidney disease on their daily life, while others are not. How much does kidney disease <b>bother</b> you in each of the following areas?",
      "kd24": "Fluid restriction?",
